title: 1.19 Numbers I: Into the Wilderness
itunes:title: Numbers I: Into the Wilderness
description: It should have been but a few days march from Mt Sinai to the promised land. But the Israelite's kvetching annoys God so much he condemns them to spend 40 years in the wilderness.
content:encoded: It should have been but a few days march from Mt Sinai to the promised land. But the Israelite's kvetching annoys God so much he condemns them to spend 40 years in the wilderness.
itunes:subtitle: The Israelites leave Sinai for the short trip to Canaan. Things don't go so well.
itunes:author: Garry Stevens
